No way no how can you bring these into the U.S.  I'm sure if you could it
would be done and I'd have one :-)
Apparently the UK has somewhat more lax vehicle requirements but in the U.S.
these vehicles would have to be DOT and EPA certified for 2002 safety and
emissions requirements.  Hmm no airbags, or side impact door beams.  I sure
don't have the money to custom-engineer and certify such systems.  The
engine is not EPA certified so good luck with that, I know it costs the
manufacturers lots of $$$ to do that.  Guaranteed you wouldn't meet 2002
emissions requirements with it.

